snippet.title: Give me toilet paper! on Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Stick your JoyCon in a toilet paper tube and roll your way to weirdo fun!

To see the game's profile page check out: https://www.nindiespotlight.com/game_profile.cfm?game=give-me-toilet-paper-switch

If you enjoy these videos, and would like to see more, please subscribe!
https://www.youtube.com/NindieSpotlight/?sub_confirmation=1

If you're simply a Nintendo fan, have a Switch, and are looking for suggestions on the best games on the system, focusing mostly on indie games, be sure to check us out at: https://www.nindiespotlight.com/

#Nintendo #NintendoSwitch #IndieGames
